Diego, it's okay.

37:08.936 --> 37:11.271
<i>Diego Maradona isn't getting up.</i>

37:12.189 --> 37:15.567
<i>Let's see what the referee decides.</i>

37:15.692 --> 37:18.403
<i>It's a yellow card for Andoni Goikoetxea,</i>

37:18.695 --> 37:21.239
<i>who isn't even expelled from the field.</i>

37:21.323 --> 37:25.577
<i>Meanwhile, Maradona</i>
<i>is writhing in pain on the ground</i>

37:25.661 --> 37:28.497
<i>and help is being requested</i>
<i>from the paramedics</i>

37:28.580 --> 37:31.249
<i>to carry the Argentine star off,</i>

37:31.333 --> 37:33.627
<i>whose face reveals excruciating pain.</i>

37:33.710 --> 37:38.215
<i>This may be a serious injury</i>
<i>for the Barcelona player,</i>

37:38.298 --> 37:43.053
<i>the star of the team, who is now</i>
<i>making his way to the changing room.</i>

37:51.186 --> 37:54.690
He broke my leg, man.
He did it on purpose.

37:54.773 --> 37:58.360
- Easy, Pelusa.
- It hurts so much.

37:58.443 --> 38:02.531
You've been on the ground for 20 minutes.
Where's the ambulance?

38:02.656 --> 38:05.867
- Why isn't the ambulance here?
- They did it on purpose.

39:11.391 --> 39:14.978
<i>The drama between President</i>
<i>Josep Lluís Núñez and Diego Maradona</i>

39:15.062 --> 39:18.440
<i>got a new chapter this week,</i>
<i>when the Barcelona star</i>

39:18.523 --> 39:21.443
<i>traveled to Argentina</i>
<i>to begin his rehabilitation there.</i>

39:22.903 --> 39:25.614
<i>Maradona ignored warnings</i>
<i>from the club's leaders,</i>

39:25.697 --> 39:28.867
<i>who wanted to have his injury</i>
<i>treated by the club's doctors.</i>

39:28.950 --> 39:30.535
They injured me.

39:30.660 --> 39:34.956
<i>The individual who has taken on</i>
<i>rehabilitating Diego in Argentina</i>

39:35.040 --> 39:39.503
<i>is one Dr. Rubén Oliva,</i>
<i>famous for his unorthodox methods.</i>

39:43.715 --> 39:47.385
The doctors at Barcelona say
that Diego should keep the cast on

39:47.469 --> 39:50.597
and not walk on it.
We're gonna do the exact opposite.

39:51.181 --> 39:54.392
A fracture like this can't be fixed
by immobilizing it,

39:54.476 --> 39:57.104
because the tissues will not regenerate.

39:57.187 --> 39:58.730
It's time to walk on it.

39:59.731 --> 40:01.149
The body has memory,

40:01.233 --> 40:03.652
and you'll be able to recover your talent.

40:03.735 --> 40:07.823
Okay, excuse me, Dieguito.
Come on, there you go.

40:07.906 --> 40:09.908
- Let's go, come on.
- Careful, Carlos.

40:09.991 --> 40:12.244
- Come on.
- Carlos, not like that!

40:12.327 --> 40:14.162
- Carlos.
- Be strong, Diego.

40:14.246 --> 40:15.872
The World Cup is coming up.

40:28.802 --> 40:31.054
Let's eat! It's ready!

40:37.978 --> 40:39.938
Let's eat, leave the ball alone.

40:40.939 --> 40:42.399
Hit me.

40:44.151 --> 40:45.402
I win.

41:21.229 --> 41:22.731
How are you, Mr. Francis?

41:23.315 --> 41:24.441
Do you remember me?

41:26.610 --> 41:27.777
Hey, Pelusa!

41:28.445 --> 41:30.197
What are you doing here?

41:31.114 --> 41:32.449
No!

41:32.991 --> 41:34.659
What are you doing here?

41:37.329 --> 41:40.874
Hey, kid, how's it going?

41:40.957 --> 41:43.460
Just hanging out. I got injured.

41:43.960 --> 41:46.129
I need you to teach me how to kick.

41:47.964 --> 41:52.135
Hit that asshole between the eyes,
so he remembers that this is a game.

41:59.684 --> 42:02.312
When you hit it, don't pull away so fast.

42:02.395 --> 42:04.105
The ball won't know what you want.

42:07.692 --> 42:09.986
I don't want to hear noise, Pelusa.

42:16.159 --> 42:17.869
Show me your shoe.

42:19.871 --> 42:22.749
Kid, your ankle's changed.
It's a different ankle.

42:22.832 --> 42:25.752
You have to bandage it differently.
Take it off.

42:32.550 --> 42:33.677
Try it like this.

42:35.804 --> 42:38.890
- Do you think this is going to work?
- God knows.

42:50.110 --> 42:51.945
That's it!

42:52.028 --> 42:54.239
You're going to be all right, kid!

42:55.323 --> 42:57.993
<i>The end of corruption!</i>

43:00.829 --> 43:03.623
<i>The end of Argentina's helplessness...</i>

43:03.707 --> 43:06.876
<i>Democracy is coming to the country!</i>

43:08.461 --> 43:10.964
Hey, come on! Turn off the TV.

43:11.047 --> 43:14.467
Stop being so miserable.
Come here, it's Diego's birthday.

43:14.634 --> 43:17.220
<i>It's basically about</i>

43:17.304 --> 43:20.765
<i>seeing if it's possible for us...</i>

43:23.101 --> 43:25.770
- Come on, Dad, come on.
- Honey!

43:32.569 --> 43:33.987
Your attention, please.

43:34.904 --> 43:36.948
Hey, I want to make a toast,

43:37.032 --> 43:39.117
to democracy and to Alfonsín.

43:39.701 --> 43:41.494
- Cheers!
- Cheers.

43:42.329 --> 43:45.707
And also to Argentina
qualifying for the World Cup

43:45.790 --> 43:47.792
and being world champions.

43:48.293 --> 43:51.129
<i>Argentina, Argentina!</i>

43:51.212 --> 43:53.673
<i>Argentina, Argentina!</i>

43:53.757 --> 43:56.176
<i>Argentina, Argentina!</i>

45:00.865 --> 45:01.991
Lorena, have you...

45:04.160 --> 45:06.037
been with other guys lately?

45:08.623 --> 45:10.458
Why are you asking me that, Diego?

45:11.167 --> 45:14.129
You're doing things in bed
that you didn't do before.

45:15.213 --> 45:16.631
Of course, I have.

45:17.048 --> 45:18.925
Are you saying I can't?

45:19.092 --> 45:20.760
We're not a couple.

45:20.844 --> 45:22.137
So, what are we?

45:22.220 --> 45:24.013
I don't know, you tell me.

45:24.222 --> 45:26.349
Every time the press asks you about me,

45:26.433 --> 45:28.351
you pretend to be offended.

45:28.435 --> 45:30.854
- I don't want to hurt Claudia.
- That's fine.

45:31.521 --> 45:34.315
Because Claudia is your girlfriend,
isn't she?

45:35.316 --> 45:36.734
Claudia is a good girl

45:36.985 --> 45:39.612
who is willing to follow you everywhere,

45:39.863 --> 45:41.531
to put up with your affairs.

45:42.490 --> 45:43.616
I'm not.

45:45.118 --> 45:47.745
You never asked me not to have affairs.

45:47.829 --> 45:49.414
And I never will.

45:50.331 --> 45:52.208
Because I want to have them too.

45:52.959 --> 45:54.919
I won't give up anything for you.

45:59.507 --> 46:01.634
I think it's best that we break this off.

46:04.637 --> 46:05.972
Are you leaving now?

46:28.077 --> 46:30.455
<i>We are at the Santiago Bernabeu Stadium.</i>

46:30.538 --> 46:33.666
<i>It's the '83-'84 Copa del Rey final,</i>

46:33.750 --> 46:36.085
<i>FC Barcelona, Athletic Bilbao.</i>

46:36.169 --> 46:39.255
<i>The Royal Family waves.</i>
<i>The game is about to begin.</i>

46:39.339 --> 46:42.592
<i>There's Barcelona's president,</i>
<i>the Bilbao supporters.</i>

46:45.803 --> 46:47.805
<i>The players are lined up.</i>

46:49.724 --> 46:51.684
I swear I didn't mean to hurt you.

46:51.768 --> 46:55.730
When I heard about your fracture,
I called you several times to apologize.

46:55.813 --> 46:57.565
Take your hand off me, idiot.

46:57.649 --> 47:01.277
You shouldn't be here.
You should be in a zoo, donkey.

47:01.361 --> 47:03.947
I'll make you eat grass.
You'll see, donkey.

47:04.614 --> 47:05.657
Let it go, man.

47:06.157 --> 47:08.493
<i>There's César Luis Menotti on the bench,</i>

47:08.576 --> 47:11.329
<i>the players posing for the press.</i>

47:12.747 --> 47:15.041
<i>The champions, Athletic Bilbao,</i>

47:15.124 --> 47:17.001
<i>and the game is about to start.</i>

47:18.253 --> 47:21.589
<i>First whistle. They're playing</i>
<i>for the Copa del Rey at Bernabeu.</i>

47:21.714 --> 47:23.341
<i>Maradona has the ball.</i>

47:24.509 --> 47:28.096
<i>There goes Maradona. Foul from Liceranzu.</i>

47:28.471 --> 47:31.891
<i>A pass to the goal area.</i>
<i>Endika and it's a goal for Bilbao.</i>

47:31.975 --> 47:35.436
<i>They take the lead,</i>
<i>Athletic Bilbao with Endika.</i>

47:35.520 --> 47:37.772
<i>Maradona, foul from Liceranzu.</i>

47:37.855 --> 47:40.108
<i>Liceranzu against Maradona.</i>

47:40.233 --> 47:43.361
<i>Another impact from Liceranzu</i>
<i>against Diego Maradona.</i>

47:43.444 --> 47:46.823
<i>The Argentine star tries to shoot,</i>
<i>he gets a foul.</i>

47:46.906 --> 47:49.742
<i>It's Maradona again.</i>
<i>Liceranzu is down, an impact.</i>

47:50.618 --> 47:53.746
<i>Barcelona can't get through,</i>
<i>another foul from Liceranzu.</i>

47:53.830 --> 47:56.708
<i>Schuster gets mad</i>
<i>and complains to the audience</i>

47:56.791 --> 47:58.960
<i>and expresses all of his anger.</i>

47:59.794 --> 48:02.714
<i>Barcelona is losing</i>
<i>in this Copa del Rey final.</i>

48:02.797 --> 48:05.216
<i>It's Maradona,</i>
<i>and he's down, another impact.</i>

48:05.341 --> 48:06.718
<i>It's Liceranzu again.</i>

48:06.801 --> 48:11.222
<i>Maradona, angry and upset,</i>
<i>confronts his rival.</i>

48:11.306 --> 48:14.684
<i>The referee splits them up,</i>
<i>and so ends the game.</i>

48:14.767 --> 48:18.271
<i>Athletic Bilbao is</i>
<i>the new Copa del Rey champion,</i>

48:18.354 --> 48:21.065
<i>and it ends with them coming to blows.</i>

48:21.149 --> 48:24.569
<i>Maradona, out of control,</i>
<i>maybe remembering</i>

48:24.652 --> 48:28.448
<i>that this was the team that forced him</i>
<i>off the field for several months.</i>

48:28.531 --> 48:30.992
<i>Andoni Goikoetxea is part of the team.</i>

48:31.451 --> 48:35.830
<i>This has become a boxing match</i>
<i>on the soccer field.</i>

48:35.913 --> 48:38.833
<i>They're trying to split up</i>
<i>Diego Armando Maradona</i>

48:38.916 --> 48:41.377
<i>and some of the injured ones.</i>

48:41.461 --> 48:45.256
<i>Athletic Bilbao crowned champions</i>
<i>in an embarrassing Copa del Rey final.</i>

48:49.844 --> 48:53.973
I want Maradona out of Barca,
out of Catalonia and out of Spain!

48:54.641 --> 48:57.435
Look, Jorge,
the club's board of directors,

48:58.227 --> 49:02.106
after quite a few hours of discussion,
has unanimously decided

49:02.190 --> 49:05.652
that Diego Armando Maradona's tenure
at Barcelona is over.

49:06.653 --> 49:08.863
We will make it official immediately,

49:08.946 --> 49:11.699
so that we can hear offers
from other clubs.

49:14.535 --> 49:18.498
- There's no way to rectify this situation?
- There's no turning back.

49:26.255 --> 49:31.135
Well, gentlemen, if that's all.

49:51.864 --> 49:53.074
Cheers, cheers.

49:56.703 --> 49:59.247
Oh, my God, they're crazy.

50:01.124 --> 50:03.584
What's up? Are you enjoying the sausages?

50:03.668 --> 50:06.212
Your girlfriend is beautiful,
congratulations.

50:06.295 --> 50:07.630
Hey, how are you?

50:08.047 --> 50:12.635
That looks so good.
The sausages are really good.

50:13.761 --> 50:16.472
Hello, how are you? All good?

50:16.556 --> 50:19.475
Waiter, over there.
Make sure no one's hungry.

50:19.559 --> 50:21.519
Hi, thanks for coming.

50:21.602 --> 50:23.396
Thanks for coming. Nice hair.

50:25.356 --> 50:27.734
What's up, Rengo? Is that how you dance?

50:27.817 --> 50:30.570
Be careful of Rengo,
because Rengo has a big one,

50:30.653 --> 50:33.364
and he's horny as hell. Excuse me.

50:33.448 --> 50:36.868
Come on, say a few words, Pelusa, come on.

50:36.951 --> 50:40.121
Everyone wants to hear you
say a few words.

50:40.246 --> 50:44.792
Speech, speech, speech, speech!

50:45.877 --> 50:49.380
Well, friends, I invited you here today...

50:51.299 --> 50:53.676
to blow the roof off this place!

50:55.595 --> 50:58.181
That's what we say
when we throw a great party,

50:58.264 --> 51:01.976
and today we have to celebrate because...

51:03.102 --> 51:05.229
I was kicked off the Barcelona team.

51:08.483 --> 51:11.277
It was a shitty time in my life, you know?

51:12.320 --> 51:14.947
I had a bad time.
They gave me a hard time.

51:15.031 --> 51:18.159
So everything from here on out
will be so much better.

51:19.327 --> 51:24.207
I want to thank my friends,
my lifelong friends, who came with me.

51:24.540 --> 51:26.793
I wouldn't be here without them.

51:27.418 --> 51:29.003
We love you, Pelusa!

51:29.253 --> 51:32.256
And especially
I want to thank Claudia, who...

51:32.340 --> 51:35.510
You are my love. I love you.
You are the love of my life.

51:35.593 --> 51:38.179
But I don't want to bore you,
so enjoy and dance.

51:43.351 --> 51:45.186
You're beautiful. I love you.

51:45.269 --> 51:46.145
- Really?
- Yes.

51:49.524 --> 51:50.775
Diego, stop.

51:51.150 --> 51:52.735
- I need to pee.
- Yeah?

51:52.819 --> 51:54.987
Yes, I'm about to burst.

51:58.991 --> 52:00.868
Let's celebrate.

52:00.952 --> 52:04.080
You two, what are you doing?
Take it easy, huh? Excuse me.

52:04.705 --> 52:06.582
Hello, my dear.

52:08.918 --> 52:10.336
Don't go too far.

52:11.170 --> 52:12.088
Okay.

52:13.381 --> 52:16.133
Excuse me. Who's next for the bathroom?

52:16.342 --> 52:17.802
I'll cut in, it's my house,

52:17.885 --> 52:20.096
I'm not going to wait, guys, thanks.

52:20.972 --> 52:22.098
Excuse me.

52:24.517 --> 52:29.105
- I didn't know you were here.
- It's all right, don't worry.

52:31.148 --> 52:34.277
Hey, tell me, is it true what they say?

52:35.403 --> 52:38.656
If you do it once,
you become a drug addict forever?

52:39.198 --> 52:41.909
If that were the case,
half the population of Spain

52:41.993 --> 52:44.579
would be in rehab by now.

52:47.206 --> 52:49.750
- Could I try some?
- Sure.

52:52.044 --> 52:54.589
Really? Is this your first time?

52:57.008 --> 52:58.092
Well.

52:59.594 --> 53:02.597
Press on one side
and inhale with the other.

53:02.680 --> 53:04.599
Don't blow out, or you'll waste it.

53:21.407 --> 53:22.867
It stings a little, huh?

53:31.375 --> 53:35.296
At Barcelona, Diego Maradona
played 58 games and scored 38 goals.

53:35.379 --> 53:38.341
With him the club won the Copa del Rey,

53:38.424 --> 53:41.844
the Copa de la Liga and Spain's Supercopa.

53:43.346 --> 53:46.849
The final against Athletic Bilbao
that ended in a battlefield

53:46.933 --> 53:48.893
hurried his departure from the club.

53:50.311 --> 53:53.356
Josep Núñez was in charge
of the club for 22 years.

53:53.439 --> 53:56.901
In 2011, he was accused
and sentenced to 6 years in prison

53:56.984 --> 53:58.569
for bribery and tax evasion.

53:59.987 --> 54:01.781
After injuring Maradona,

54:01.864 --> 54:05.159
Goikoetxea earned the nickname,
"The Butcher of Bilbao."

54:05.242 --> 54:08.412
He still keeps the shoes
he wore during that game.

54:09.455 --> 54:12.667
Maradona, what does
César Menotti's Barcelona have

54:12.750 --> 54:14.126
that Lattek's didn't?

54:14.210 --> 54:17.713
There are other ways to see the future.

54:17.797 --> 54:20.841
We all want to earn our place
because we know

54:20.925 --> 54:24.804
we are in a hurry because
of the great players we have

54:25.388 --> 54:28.349
off the field and that makes us

54:28.724 --> 54:31.644
want to show Menotti that we can deliver.

54:44.490 --> 54:47.368
<i>I'm sad because I'd never been injured</i>

54:48.619 --> 54:51.163
in the six years
before I came to Barcelona,

54:51.247 --> 54:53.374
playing in the first division.

54:53.457 --> 54:56.002
I'd never been injured, never been sick,

54:56.544 --> 55:00.006
and I came to Barcelona
with a great desire

55:00.089 --> 55:03.259
to win many championships,

55:03.342 --> 55:05.136
and I didn't even play a full one.

55:13.102 --> 55:15.730
I feel so proud to have been chosen,

55:16.480 --> 55:19.692
because, let's be clear,
I didn't teach Diego, he was a genius,

55:19.817 --> 55:22.319
I took care of him
so that he could succeed.

55:32.747 --> 55:34.915
What does this victory mean to you?

55:34.999 --> 55:38.002
Personally, it means a lot,

55:38.085 --> 55:41.630
because we weren't aiming for it.

55:41.714 --> 55:44.133
We just got lucky.

55:44.216 --> 55:47.261
Today, on the other hand,
we made an unlucky mistake

55:47.344 --> 55:49.889
and Madrid drew without deserving it,

55:49.972 --> 55:52.641
but in the end, I think that we did it,

55:52.725 --> 55:55.853
and, thank God, we won the Copa del Rey.

56:03.778 --> 56:05.821
I want to say to the people of Barcelona

56:05.905 --> 56:07.531
that not all Argentines are bad.

56:07.907 --> 56:09.992
We don't tear anybody down

56:10.076 --> 56:11.744
and we know how to live.

56:11.827 --> 56:14.747
We are not accountable

56:14.830 --> 56:17.416
for those who came here to harm Barcelona,

56:17.500 --> 56:21.921
but we're being made to pay for it.

56:22.254 --> 56:25.007
A lot happened, I made mistakes,

56:25.091 --> 56:30.012
but I was always upfront,
I never hid anything.
